layout.house_prompt: This bedroom has a full-size bed against a wall with a cartoon painting above. Two nightstands on each side of the bed provide storage. A writing desk in the corner holds a modern lamp for task lighting. A large wardrobe stands next to the door for additional storage. Beside the bedroom is a cozy living room with a large sofa facing a sleek coffee table where puzzles and decorative coasters reside. A bookshelf in the corner displays books and family pictures. The stylish bathroom includes a bathtub, with a toilet in the corner. The vanity features a double sink, with toiletries and white candles on top. A wicker basket at the foot of the bathtub holds towels.

hallway.text_description: A cozy modern entry hallway/foyer with clean lines and simple decor, compact and efficient for circulation, connecting the living room, bedroom, and bathroom.

bathroom.text_description: A stylish cozy-modern bathroom with a bathtub, a toilet in the corner, and a vanity with a double sink. Toiletries and white candles sit on the vanity, and a wicker basket at the foot of the bathtub holds towels.

bedroom.text_description: A cozy modern bedroom beside the living room with a full-size bed against a wall and a cartoon painting above it, two nightstands (one on each side) for storage, a writing desk in the corner with a modern task lamp, and a large wardrobe positioned next to the bedroom door for additional storage.

living_room.text_description: A cozy modern living room beside the bedroom, featuring a large comfortable sofa facing a sleek coffee table that holds puzzles and decorative coasters, plus a bookshelf in the corner displaying books and family pictures.
